jobs.description:
Joined as a Asst.Director at GJEPC on 2011. The major responsibilities are:
•	Handling all Export/Import issues, Trade Policy and Procedure,    Service Tax, VAT, Octroi issues, etc.;
•	Administering research projects, programmes, conferences and other institutional activities; 
•	Contributing in organizing the National/International exhibitions, Buy-Seller meeting;
•	Managing the networking with all the Government Departments ;
•	Involved in liaising  with DGFT, DGST, Banks, RBI, MoC&I, ECGC, Customs etc; 
•	Facilitating the trade by guiding the member exporters and representing their issues in the relevant Government Departments behalf of the Council. 
•	Analysis to find out the focus and potential markets, NTB and SPS barriers in that market, to find out the competitor in the focus market etc.
